和经典爱情故事的方式，以及人际关系的真正复杂性。</p><p> “当我准备放弃时，我被带入这个家园，并被阳光、友谊、食物、快乐、动物、自然所治愈，并爱上了一个你真正意想不到的人，这让我从一个破碎的人变成了一个人。” ，对更高层次的自我（在本例中是仙女）来说该死的混乱。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="凯特·纳什谈“Misery”、心理健康和“GLOW”的未来" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GRbUEUPWVME?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2> <strong>“9悲伤交响曲”的曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>《数以百万计的心跳》<br /></strong> <strong>&#39;苦难&#39;<br /></strong> <strong>“废人”<br /></strong> <strong>&#39;弃&#39;<br /></strong> <strong>‘马’<br /></strong> <strong>“我的胆汁”<br /></strong> <strong>“这些感受”<br /></strong> <strong>《太空漫游2001》<br /></strong> <strong>&#39;射线&#39;<br /></strong> <strong>“吸血鬼”</strong></p><p>纳什今年将在伦敦演出两场头条秀：5 月 17 日的 EarthH 和 11 月 28 日的 KOKO <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/kate-nash-tickets/artist/1179996?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkHWi51ncSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">。在这里查找剩余的门票</a>。</p><p> 2024 年的其他预定日期包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/caity-baser-lulu-frank-turner-and-skindred-among-new-names-for-glastonbury-2024-line-up-in-field-of-avalon-reveal-3618404#:~:text=Others%20confirmed%20for%20the%202024,Spraggan%2C%20The%20Feeling%20and%20more.">Glastonbury Festival</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-paolo-nutini-and-the-streets-to-headline-kendal-calling-2024-festival-line-up-buy-tickets-3576710">Kendal Calling</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-streets-and-maisie-peters-lead-new-names-for-boardmasters-2024-buy-tickets-3611707">Boardmasters</a> 。</p><p>继 2018 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kate-nash-yesterday-was-forever-2280179#:~:text=The%20moments%20of%20saving%20grace,and%20made%20for%20the%20fans.">《Yesterday Was Forever》</a>之后，纳什即将推出的新专辑还将收录最近的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kate-nash-shares-whimsical-new-single-millions-of-heartbeats-and-announces-first-album-in-nine-years-3600223">《Millions Of Heartbeats》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-kate-nashs-romantic-new-single-space-odyssey-2001-3619044">聆听 Kate Nash 的浪漫新单曲“Space Odyssey 2001”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
